data.description: Start your new year off in this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Freeman Estates! Spacious, open concept downstairs is perfect for entertaining. Gorgeous kitchen with beautiful stained cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and walk in pantry is open to the dining area and large family room. 4 generously sized bedrooms upstairs, including the master bedroom with walk in closet and master bathroom. Separate laundry room also on the upper level. This community also has a nice little park/playground that's fun for the family. Come and make this your new home!
